7. Their marriage was arranged by their parents in India. ; Photo, Michelle and 
Barry Linson and their four children, clockwise from top left, Alana, 18 
months; Shmuel, 2 months; Shira, 8; and Avigayil, 3. HYUNGWON KANG / For The 
