WESTSIDE DIGEST: WEST HOLLYWOOD; 
</P>
<P>
SANTA MONICA BLVD. CLOSURES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Nighttime street repairs on Santa Monica Boulevard between La Brea Avenue and 
Doheny Drive will cause lane closures for about a week starting Monday. The 
closures will last from 10:30 a.m. to 5 p.m. At least one lane will be open in 
each direction at all times. For more information, call 972-7098. 
