FORCES -- GERMANY; FRANCE -- ARMED FORCES -- GERMANY; INTERNMENT CAMPS; BOOKS; 
WRITERS; RESEARCH; BACQUE, JAMES; FEUDS; HISTORIANS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
