SECESSION; LITHUANIA -- GOVERNMENT; LITHUANIA -- GOVERNMENT; LATVIA -- 
GOVERNMENT; ECONOMIC SANCTIONS; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- LITHUANIA 
</P>
