Irvine?' " says Bill Graham. "If people come and loiter and leave garbage or 
urinate in public or challenge the law, then goodby to the facility." ROBERT 
GABRIEL / Los Angeles Times; Photo, DEAD RECKONING: Thanks to a few rowdy 
Deadheads, the Grateful Dead's concert future is in jeopardy, promoter Bill 
Graham warned. 
</P>
